  "text": "Corollary C. Skew-angled Coxeter systems whose diagram has no spike which is labelled by twice an odd number are rigid up to diagram twisting (in the sense of [CITATION_1] ); they are strongly rigid (in the sense of [CITATION_2] ), if there are at least 3 generators and the diagram is edge-connected.",
